home.title: Before taking the test
home.desc: Please note that this isn’t a survey, and these aren’t questions, they’re propositions. Your responses should not be overthought. Some of them are intentionally vague. Their purpose is to trigger reactions in the mind, measuring feelings and prejudices rather than detailed opinions on policy.
